  ('en', 'Abeilles du rucher', 'Which bee is the big beekeeping favorite in Europe ?', 'Black bee', 'Red bee', 'Blue bee', 'White bee', '2', 'Its original range stretched from western Russia to northern Europe and possibly the Iberian Peninsula.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_dark_bee'),
