  ('en', 'Abeilles du rucher', 'What animated film tells the life of a freshly graduated bee ?', '« Bee Movie »', '« Rosa »', '« Happy Feet »', '« Le Lorax »', '2', 'This animated film in computer graphics released in 2007 was written and produced by Jerry Seinfeld for DreamWorks SKG.', ''),
  ('en', 'Abeilles du rucher', 'In which resin were the oldest bee fossils found ?', 'Amber', 'Turquoise', 'Jet', 'Opal', '3', 'The oldest fossil to date is Melittosphex burmensis, dated 100 million years ago and discovered in 2006 in Burma.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amber'),
  ('en', 'Abeilles du rucher', 'How many castes does a bee colony consist of ?', 'Three', 'Four', 'Five', 'Six', '3', 'The queen, the only fertile female in the group, a majority of workers and males (or drones) who fertilize future queens.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bee'),
  ('en', 'Abeilles du rucher', 'Which bees use galleries dug in the wood ?', 'Xylicoles', 'Rubicoles', 'Horticultural', 'Wineries', '3', 'A xylophagus is a living organism whose diet consists mainly of sapwood, but also of perfect wood.', ''),
